summary:
Replaces texture of the eyes for Human Races in Skyrim.
The Concept is little more realistic and cute than Vanilla.
descriptionHtml:
日本語の[url=http://skyrimshot.blog.fc2.com/blog-entry-5.html]説明[/url]
My blog [url=https://skyrimshot.blogspot.com/2017/06/cute-eyes.html]Article[/url]

[color=#ffd966][size=3][b]What is this?[/b][/size][/color]

Replaces texture of the eyes for Human Races in Skyrim.
The Concept is little more realistic and cute than Vanilla.

Irises colors like vanilla a little bigger(x1.02).This position is slightly lower.
Clean(less bloodshot) and bright white of eyes.
Natural Inner
Corners of Eyes.
Natural Eyelashes.
More reflective gloss Eyes.
http://skyrimshot.blog.fc2.com/blog-entry-5.html

Not include Beast and Elves Eyes.


Files have been modified.
